### What happens?

Dear DuckDB developers,
I meet some unexpected results, please see the below cases.
```sql
CREATE TABLE t0(c0 INT);
CREATE TABLE t1(c0 INT);
CREATE TABLE t2(c0 INT);

INSERT INTO t0(c0) VALUES (1);
INSERT INTO t1(c0) VALUES (0);
INSERT INTO t2(c0) VALUES (0);

SELECT * FROM  t2 INNER  JOIN t0 ON (NOT((t0.c0)<(t2.c0))) WHERE 'duckdb';
-- Conversion Error:
-- Could not convert string 'duckdb' to BOOL

SELECT * FROM  t2 SEMI  JOIN t1 ON ((t2.c0)>=(t1.c0)) WHERE 'duckdb';
-- Conversion Error:
-- Could not convert string 'duckdb' to BOOL

-- However,  WHERE 'duckdb' are executed as true in the following join.
SELECT * FROM  t2 INNER  JOIN t0 ON (NOT((t0.c0)<(t2.c0))) SEMI  JOIN t1 ON ((t2.c0)>=(t1.c0)) WHERE ('duckdb');
-- 0, 1

```

